title: Looking for the perfect home?
posting_body: ['Text 1268C for more info!', 'East Riverside, Austin Luxury Apartments', 'Looking for the perfect home?', 'Search no more – at  South Shore Apartments, perks after perks blend to create the ideal nest for you.', 'These luxury apartments in Riverside, Austin, were thoughtfully designed to impress, providing everything one could wish for.', 'When it comes to our East Riverside, Austin luxury apartments, comfort, space, and style are top priorities.', 'And they are all ensured by our long list of amenities.', 'Step inside these homes through the smart entries and admire the high ceilings.', 'Stainless-steel appliances and quartz countertops are the norm in our kitchens, where everything is lit up by pendant lighting.', 'The ambience wraps you in daily comforts, thanks to the smart thermostats and ceiling fans.', 'The large walk-in closets are convenient when it comes to storing your cherished belongings.', 'What’s more, the 8-foot doors and huge balconies and patios are there to prove that our community is all about generosity.', 'Plus, full-size washers and dryers make laundry days go smoothly.', 'Pampering sessions in the bathroom become the highlight of your day, thanks to the 42-inch soaking tubs and frameless showers.', 'Cats and dogs are both welcome – but did we tell you that all breeds, ages, and sizes are allowed?', 'Life at South Shore Apartments stays awesome, even outside the comfort of our apartments in Riverside, Austin, TX.', 'And that is because a dog run is provided, as well as garage parking.', 'Secured access control to all entries makes you feel safe and sound, and you can’t go wrong when you have all kinds of shops on the ground floor.']
